## Launch `st` Terminals with Same CWD

you need to enable `NEWTERM_PATCH` and `WORKINGDIR_PATCH` and `OSC7_PATCH` patches in `st-flexipatch` first

then you also need to enable `SPAWNCMD_PATCH` from `dwm-flexipatch`

then from dwm config for launching `st` use

